\newlabel{fig:ho_numerov_vs_rk4}{{14}{8}{Comparison of Numerov and RK4 shooting for the harmonic oscillator. Both methods show fourth-order convergence, while Numerov gives a smaller maximum energy error at the same grid spacing}{figure.caption.5}{}}
